metadata.name: Smugbunny: Be Like Water
metadata.description:
Get ready for an epic adventure with Smugbunny! Recently, the Chinese Discord community inspired me to make a Kung fu animation featuring our lovable Smugbunny. I couldn't resist dressing them up in Bruce Lee's iconic track suit and training them with a secret time-stopping spin kick!

Smugbunny truly embodies Bruce Lee's philosophy of being like water, flowing effortlessly and adapting to any situation. Join Smugbunny in their hidden kwoon and get ready to bounce together as they train to fight the giant evil robot!
